    "attributes": {
        "action": "Reduce council tax by 50% for single persons",
        "additional_details": "I feel this should be done due to the cost of living, increases in tax and the pressure of single people and single parents face.\r\n \r\nI believe we have the same bills as everyone else but with only 1 wage coming in.\r\n \r\nI think the single person discount should be set at 50% which would be fair considering you are single and not in a couple.",
        "background": "I think that the single persons council tax discount should be set at 50% reduction instead of 25%.",
